Habitat and distribution
. Benthopelagic to benthic on the lower slope, continental rise and upper abyss, between 1,100 and 
3,300 m
depth and primarily between 2 and 4ºC isotherm (
Sulak 1990
). Circumglobal at tropical and temperate latitudes. Western Atlantic, from Canada to Venezuela and Guyana; eastern Atlantic, off northwestern Africa, Azores Islands and the Gulf of Guinea (
Sulak 1977
, 
1990
); Indian Ocean, from Saya-de- Malaya Bank and the East Indian Range (
Filatova 1985
), and eastern, central and northern Pacific Ocean and waters off of Chile (
Froese & Sampang 2004
; 
Kamikawa & Stevenson 2010
; 

Hanke 
et al
. 2014

).
